Calibrate device (center, DOR, pedals)

Usage: wheelctl device calibrate [OPTIONS] <DEVICE> <CALIBRATION_TYPE>

Arguments:
  <DEVICE>            Device ID or name
  <CALIBRATION_TYPE>  Calibration type [possible values: center, dor, pedals, all]

Options:
      --json        Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -y, --yes         Skip interactive prompts
  -v, --verbose...  Verbose logging
  -h, --help        Print help
